1. 问题: 统计每个分类下不同首字母（小写）的演员姓氏数量，并只保留姓氏首字母为a-c的分组
   原始错误: 语法错误 在 ")" 或附近的
LINE 1: ...(SUBSTRING(a.last_name, 1, 1)) BETWEEN 'a' AND 'c') ORDER BY...
                                                             ^
   修复后SQL:
   SELECT c.name AS 分类名称, LOWER(SUBSTRING(a.last_name, 1, 1)) AS 姓氏首字母, COUNT(DISTINCT a.actor_id) AS 演员人数 FROM public.category c JOIN public.film_category fc ON c.category_id = fc.category_id JOIN public.film_actor fa ON fc.film_id = fa.film_id JOIN public.actor a ON fa.actor_id = a.actor_id GROUP BY c.name, LOWER(SUBSTRING(a.last_name, 1, 1)) HAVING LOWER(SUBSTRING(a.last_name, 1, 1)) BETWEEN 'a' AND 'c' ORDER BY 分类名称, 姓氏首字母;
----------------------------------------

2. 问题: 找出尚未归还的租赁记录总数、平均租赁时长（从租赁日至今的天数）及最久未归还天数
   原始错误: 函数 round(interval, integer) 不存在
LINE 1: EXPLAIN SELECT COUNT(*) AS 未归还总数, ROUND(AVG(CURRENT_DAT...
                                               ^
HINT:  没有匹配指定名称和参数类型的函数. 您也许需要增加明确的类型转换.
   修复后SQL:
   SELECT COUNT(*) AS 未归还总数, ROUND(AVG(CURRENT_DATE - rental_date::date), 1) AS 平均租赁天数, MAX(CURRENT_DATE - rental_date::date) AS 最久未归还天数 FROM public.rental WHERE return_date IS NULL;
----------------------------------------

3. 问题: 列出每家门店（通过员工所属门店）的年度收款总额，按2007年降序排列
   原始错误: trailing junk after numeric literal 在 "2007年收款总额" 或附近的
LINE 1: ...IN SELECT st.store_id AS 店铺ID, SUM(p.amount) AS 2007年收款...
                                                             ^
   修复后SQL:
   SELECT st.store_id AS 店铺ID, SUM(p.amount) AS "2007年收款总额" FROM public.payment p JOIN public.staff st ON p.staff_id = st.staff_id WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM p.payment_date) = 2007 GROUP BY st.store_id ORDER BY "2007年收款总额" DESC;
----------------------------------------
